details.description:
All structure elements shall belong to, or be role mapped to, at least one of the following
            namespaces specified in ISO 32000-2:2020, 14.8.6:
            — the PDF 1.7 namespace;
            — the PDF 2.0 namespace;
            — the MathML namespace

